data.description: Alluring rural lifestyle awaits you on this versatile & picturesque 6 acre property! Modern meets rustic in this beautifully upgraded 1,701 SqFt rambler featuring a spacious primary bedroom with en suite (soaking tub, dual vanity, & walk-in closet) & 2 additional guest bedrooms + 1 full guest bathroom.  Open concept living room w/ gas fireplace, bright & inviting dining room, and kitchen with ample storage + walk-in pantry. Outdoors you'll enjoy a large deck & back yard perfect for entertaining, sprawling irrigated pastures & a 36x36 barn/shop+finished room & 60x24 hay/machine shed. Close proximity to Yakima River, outdoor hobbies/activities - yet moments from downtown Ellensburg & easy access to I-90.
